## 💡 Key Design Patterns to Consider

| Pattern | Where to Use |
|---------|--------------|
| **Strategy Pattern** | Pricing (different rates for car types) |
| **State Pattern** | Booking lifecycle (Reserved → Active → Completed → Cancelled) |
| **Factory Pattern** | Creating different car types |
| **Singleton** | RentalService, InventoryManager |

